          <li>What are the coordinates of the basis vectors? How about their images under <m>D</m>?</li>
          <li>Verify that when the matrix for <m>D</m> is applied to the coordinate vector for <m>x^2 - x -1</m> that the coordinate vector for <m>2x-1</m> is obtained.</li>
